  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2019-05-16",
    "date": "2020-02-13T17:13:35Z",
    "text": "Help Students Vote Act\n\nThis bill addresses voter registration\u00a0of students who attend\u00a0institutions of higher education (IHEs) that participate in federal student aid programs.\n\nSpecifically, this bill (1) requires IHEs to make a good faith effort to distribute voter registration forms to each of their students at least twice a year, (2) authorizes grants to IHEs that greatly exceed the requirements governing the distribution of voter registration forms, and (3) allows civil actions against IHEs that violate the requirements."
  },
